# 🦜 Aurum – Wildlife Crime Analysis Tool

**Aurum** is an open analytical tool to detect signs of organized crime in wildlife trafficking datasets.

It uses statistical methods and unsupervised learning to analyze patterns like:

- 📈 Temporal Trends (TCS) (running)
- 🧬 Species Co-occurrence  (under construction)
- 🚨 Anomaly Detection (under construction)
- 🕸️ Network Connectivity  (under construction)
- 🧮 Organized Crime Score (OCS)  (under construction)
- 🧠 Wildlife Crime Staging (SARA Model)
